OL,3,CPope puts 'God's architect' Antoni
OL,4,CGaudi on the path to sainthood
OL,6,FIn his first act since he left
OL,7,Fhospital, the Pope has put Antoni
OL,8,FGaudi onto the first step on the
OL,9,Fladder to sainthood, ITV News
OL,10,FCorrespondent Geraint Vincent reports
OL,12,FThe Vatican announced on Monday that
OL,13,FAntoni Gaudi, long nicknamed "God's
OL,14,Farchitect", is on the path to
OL,15,Fsainthood.
OL,17,FIn a statement, the Vatican
OL,18,Facknowledged Gaudi's "heroic virtues"
OL,19,Fas explanation for the Pope's decision
OL,20,Fto make him venerable.
