OL,3,CPope puts 'God's architect' Antoni
OL,4,CGaudi on the path to sainthood
OL,6,FThe Catalan architect is best known
OL,7,Ffor designing Barcelona's iconic
OL,8,FSagrada Familia, which is set to be
OL,9,Fcompleted in 2026, more than 140 years
OL,10,Fafter construction began.
OL,12,FGaudi's legacy is tied to Catholicism
OL,13,Fand he envisioned his Basilica to be
OL,14,F"a Bible in stone" with 18 huge,
OL,15,Fspindle-shaped towers, each
OL,16,Fsymbolizing a different biblical
OL,17,Ffigure ` the 12 apostles, the four
OL,18,Fevangelists, the Virgin Mary and Jesus.
