OL,3,CPope puts 'God's architect' Antoni
OL,4,CGaudi on the path to sainthood
OL,6,FPope Francis' declaration, which comes
OL,7,Fnearly a centaury after the architects
OL,8,Fdeath, is one of the first steps in
OL,9,Fthe long and complex process towards
OL,10,Fbecoming a saint.
OL,12,FTo become a saint, a candidate
OL,13,Fnormally needs two miracles to be
OL,14,Fattributed to them, which is examined
OL,15,Fby theologians and then ultimately the
OL,16,Fdecision to canonise someone is made
OL,17,Fby the Pope.
