OL,3,CPope puts 'God's architect' Antoni
OL,4,CGaudi on the path to sainthood
OL,6,FVery few artists become saints and no
OL,7,Farchitect, in the modern understanding
OL,8,Fof the profession, has ever been
OL,9,Fcanonised so finding those miracles
OL,10,Fwill be the next step in this process.
OL,12,FFor decades, groups like the
OL,13,FAssociation for the Beatification of
OL,14,FAntoni Gaudi have been campaigning for
OL,15,Fhis recognition by the Catholic Church.
OL,17,FThe Archbishop of Barcelona took up
OL,18,Fthe cause in 2023 and submitted the
OL,19,F"positio", or key argument, for
OL,20,FGaudi's beatification to the Vatican.
