OL,3,CPope puts 'God's architect' Antoni
OL,4,CGaudi on the path to sainthood
OL,6,FAntoni Gaudi was struck by a tram and
OL,7,Fdied in 1926 when only 10%-15% of the
OL,8,FBasilica had been built.
OL,10,FWhile he dedicated the last few years
OL,11,Fof his life and career exclusively to
OL,12,Fthe Sagrada Familia, several other
OL,13,Fbuildings with his distinctive style
OL,14,Fare dotted around Barcelona, leaving
OL,15,Fhis mark on the city.
